      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "- Persist unfinished-session resume state across stop/failure, reload, history load, stale-running repair, and detached empty API replies.\n- Add Obsidian UI button inspection plus persistent hide/show/order rules for active/global/Cancip scopes.\n- Add tag listing, pin/unpin, right-sidebar unpinned hiding, and dry-run-first non-pinned tag deletion.\n- Tighten UI-rule application so active-scope hiding marks matched elements instead of globally hiding every same selector.\n- Built, installed, and reloaded the local Obsidian plugin output.",
