      "author": "arias007",
      "description": "- Stop/failure state now turns the send button into Continue so mobile tasks can resume from the latest session/tool state.\\n- Added on-demand session history, active Obsidian view, DOM snapshot, click, and input command-bus targets.\\n- AI reply links now open internal Vault files/folders through Cancip/Obsidian instead of mobile external link routing.\\n- Improved built-in PrimeTTS Chinese pinyin routing by converting CJK runs with phrase context.\\n- Built and installed the release output into the local Obsidian plugin.",
      "downloadCount": 0,
