      "author": "arias007",
      "description": "Cancip 0.1.207 switches the bundled offline TTS package to PrimeTTS v3_4.6M.\n\nChanges:\n- Default TTS provider is now auto -> builtin-prime-tts.\n- Bundles PrimeTTS v3_4.6M Chinese/English ONNX model assets under tts/prime-tts/.\n- Includes ONNX Runtime Web WASM under tts/prime-tts/ort/ so Android Obsidian can run it locally.\n- Removes the previous bundled Piper Plus large package from the default output. Piper Plus remains a manual legacy provider if assets are present.\n- Adds a reproducible prepare:prime-tts build step.\n\nSize notes:\n- PrimeTTS model files: about 19.1 MB.\n- TTS runtime folder including ONNX Runtime Web: about 32.6 MB unpacked.\n- Full plugin output: about 34.6 MB unpacked.\n- Release zip: about 21.0 MB.\n\nVerification:\n- npm run check\n- npm run build\n- node --check outputs/cancip/main.js\n- Local install to E:/note/.obsidian/plugins/cancip and Obsidian restart",
